import React from 'react'

const HearthSVG = ({ filled, style, handleClick, story }) =>
  <svg onClick={handleClick} style={style} width="55px" height="5px" viewBox="0 0 5 5" xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='35' height='35'>
    <g stroke='#f00' stroke-width='20' fill={filled ? 'red' : 'none'}>
      <path d='M140,20C 73,20 20,74 20,140 20,275 156,310 248,443 336,311 477,270 477,140 477,74 423,20 357,20 309,20 267,48 248,89 229,48 188,20 140,20Z' />
    </g>
  </svg>

export default HearthSVG
